title: Autopsy - The Life Of Karen Carpenter 2014 Dvd
description:
Autopsy - The Life Of Karen Carpenter

   One hour special shown on the E! channel
   First Air Date - Tues Oct 28th 2014  9pm
   Taped off Canadian Cable 
   Channel 62 
   running time 42:30 
   

   Recorded off my standalone Magnavox Dvd Recorder in SP (2 hour mode)
   I manually paused out the commercials, just like the old days!! :)


   The show is basically a reenactment of all of Karens problems surrounding her eating disorder/explaining the results of her autopsy.
   It really isnt anything anyone doesnt know about her unless you are new to her life. The small clips of her friends talking is probably ? the only new thing here. Its still worth having for fans that want something new and i really wanted to tape and share this! 

  if you havent read the books, Randy Schmidts ''Little Girl Blue'' thats fairly new is a good read and Ray Colemans ''Carpenters'' book that came out in the early 90s is also good. I prefer the earlier book but most people would suggest Randys book. they are both worth reading! so if this interests read the books!
 

 this is dvd quality 720 X 480 and the audio is 256 kb/s. 
 i only have standard cable so no HD going on but its def good! 


 Enjoy and share more Carpenters!
